Package: easieRstations
Type: Package
Title: Easy selection of weather stations using a shiny app and leaflet
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Adam H.", "Sparks", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "adamhsparks@gmail.com",
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0061-8359"))
Description: Provides a wEAther Station pIckER (EASIER) for 'NCEI' Global
    Summary of the Day, 'GSOD', and Australian Bureau of Meteorology, 'BOM',
    weather stations through a 'leaflet' driven 'shiny' interface to automate
    the download of selected weather stations' data using 'GSODR' or 'bomrang'.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.0)
